snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Namco Museum Vol. 1 [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
Included in this package are Bosconian, Galaga, New Rally-X, Pac-Man, Pole Position, Rally-X and Toy Pop.
Not only can you play these games, but you can also learn about them in the virtual museum mode included on the disc, including their history, art and the original arcade cabinets.

Namco Museum, Pac-Man, Galaga, Pole Position, New Rally-X, Rally X, Toy Pop, Bosconian (C) Bandai Namco
Developed by Now Production
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
